{"tid":2052326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴 【專訪 • 攬炒論】加山傳播全文 後記","createTime":"2020-06-05T12:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T12:49:01.000Z","uid":229275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4348db86dd018171fbb4c9b17af158553d470931","tid":2052326,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"【專訪 &bull; 攬炒論】Post II<br />\n<br />\n加山傳播全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/253767226039684/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109301110486297%2Fposts%2F253767226039684%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGSiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=c9c539dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/253767226039684/</a><br />\n<br />\n後記:<br />\n下面係喺訪問講過嘅少部分《攬炒論》。一於抽少少出黎留個記錄，同有興趣嘅手足一齊思考。<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n我第一次聽到同了解香港《焦土論》係2016年。<br />\n<br />\n當年我留意到Fb page  「無神論者的巴別塔」出咗個post，講焦土派主張要喺立法會選舉投白票，寧願投比獻世派或射落海都唔投比泛民，推動中共摧殘香港以換取民心覺醒嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n去到 2019 年1月，即係反送中前，「巴別塔」再一次重新整理焦土論述主張，但嗰時《焦土論》重心仍然係懲罰泛民同以焦土換取香港人覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n至於乜野係《攬炒論》？<br />\n簡單講喺《攬炒論》入面，（1）攬炒係反擊手段，而非目的；（2）目的係光復香港；（3）攬炒對象就係以香港人為敵嘅中共同佢嘅走狗。<br />\n<br />\n經過一年發展，有好多唔同嘅攬炒手法俾人提出。個人認為只要符合上述三點就係《香港攬炒論》嘅一部分。<br />\n<br />\n而我自己心目中嘅攬炒由兩大手段構成，（1）制裁中共、港共以及佢地嘅家人，等佢地失去外國護照、資產，身體力行永世留喺中國；（2）終極攬炒：取消香港關係法。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，我並唔係第一個人提出「取消香港關係法」作為反制手段嘅人。早喺2017年，陳浩天就有個聯署請求美國取消關係法，阻止共產黨透過香港去延續脆弱嘅中共玻璃政權。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《攬炒論》中嘅攬炒係帶住先破後立，置諸死地而後生嘅精神，依一點同傳統「焦土」意思有少少重疊之處。<br />\n<br />\n⋯<br />\n<br />\n我地之所以會喺816同學界搞「英美港盟，主權在民」遮打花園集會，就係為咗呢個隱含嘅戰略目的。我個人原意係想靠呢個集會呼應《美國關係法》同《中英聯合聲明》。<br />\n<br />\n當日其中一位嘉賓就係陳浩天；雖然我同佢至今仍然無交流過，但我提出邀請佢嘅原因，就係希望佢會親自將美國關係法嘅主張由佢自己把口講返出嚟，方便團隊之後嘅攬炒中共行動。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n攬炒團隊《重光計劃》眾籌突破75%！🔥<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gofundme.com/f/swhk-fundraiser\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fswhk-fundraiser&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGSiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=772738d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.gofundme.com/f/swhk-fundraiser</a><br />\n<br />\n正牌攬炒Channel🔥<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/StirFryChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStirFryChannel&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGSiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=73ee4e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/StirFryChannel</a>"},{"pid":"d757b780161696aed0ac59fa4c81d259ba453197","tid":2052326,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"出呢個post係想幫「無神論者的巴別塔」還個公道，唔好因為佢老婆係狗或者狙擊泛民，就當佢熱狗，無視佢提出嘅睇法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhenryporterbabel%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGSiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=593476aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/</a>"},{"pid":"486f1ae7ecc031413c7af48a283621334acb97d7","tid":2052326,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fc0169b784e3dec1982c93c99c6b90696939b8","tid":2052326,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"486f1ae7ecc031413c7af48a283621334acb97d7","tid":2052326,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 